{"tid":163021,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"識搵一定係搵暖男做男朋友","createTime":"2017-03-19T16:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T01:29:45.000Z","uid":41953,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4dfbb0ec583fe92452509f178dafaf076e3d676","tid":163021,"uid":41953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:21:11.000Z","msg":"識照顧人嘅男仔真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似我男朋友咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.識煮飯會做家務(仲話結左婚之後佢煮飯都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n2.我喊果時會幫我抺眼淚，喊到佢成件衫都係口水鼻涕都唔介意，仲幫我拎我抺完鼻涕嘅紙巾去扔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.會幫我洗底褲<br />\n4.從來唔會發我脾氣<br />\n5.一齊跌落地會好緊張問我有冇事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6.明明自己都凍，但就除件褸俾我著<br />\n7.我攤喺度睇電視叫佢餵我食野，雖然把口話我懶但都會餵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暖男喺香港都有市場架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未一齊之前聽佢講野已經覺得佢係一個好溫柔嘅男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b7e36c33e85fb1e7cddf8600f9a5fce2c75900","tid":163021,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:22:22.000Z","msg":"夜啦 去發夢啦"},{"pid":"e2c0de71b1aae8e50e34d53ac7f6bdae7c1cc4e7","tid":163021,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:22:35.000Z","msg":"暖你媽個閪！"},{"pid":"49601e1953b752bbb453ab269280b21a566b3784","tid":163021,"uid":76420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"美極？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b7b5e937b62e4540ab726c6f0dc454ba25eeb0","tid":163021,"uid":74146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"你老豆都唔會咁對你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5b2565b87082b29774b927f204